Women's basketball stars Brittney Griner, 23, and Glory Johnson, 24, are engaged.

Griner proposed to Johnson and both posted pictures of the event on social media, with Griner showing a photo of herself on one knee with a ring in her hand in front of Johnson on her Instagram account.

Griner plays for the WNBA's Phoenix Mercury and Johnson for the Tulsa Shock. The two are now the first professional athletes to become engaged to a player from a rival team.

